text: Joel C. Kitchens is an American veterinarian and politician. Born in Washington, D.C., Kitchens received his bachelors and doctor of veterinary medicine degrees from Ohio State University. Kitchens lives in Sturgeon Bay, Wisconsin and is a Republican. He served on the Sturgeon Bay Board of Education and was President of the Sturgeon Bay School Board.Biography On November 4, 2014, Kitchens was elected to the Wisconsin State Assembly.Currents Election Results ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:People from Sturgeon Bay, Wisconsin Category:People from Washington, D.C.
